text: Sally and Freedom () is a 1981 Swedish drama movie directed by Gunnel Lindblom (who also stars) and also starring Ewa Fröling, Hans Wigren, Leif Ahrle, Gunn Wållgren, Oscar Ljung, Svea Holst, Kim Anderzon. ==Other websites== * Category:1981 drama movies Category:Swedish drama movies
title: Sally and Freedom
